These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | tea  | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | comedy   |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball |
| Transport     | bike | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, strawberry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, superhero
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching musical movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | pineapple     | strawberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | musical  |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | taxi   | jet-ski    |

 #################################

 
